n: justify; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">取最小独立包装的被测样品于洁净的白色瓷盘中，在自然光下，垂直距离试样20cm</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">~</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">30cm</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">，观察其色泽、组织形态和杂质，用温开水漱口，品尝其滋味，并闻其气味。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0cm;\">\n<td style=\"width: 56.2pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 1.0cm;\" width=\"75\">\n<p style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">色&nbsp;&nbsp; 泽</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 290.6pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 1.0cm;\" width=\"387\">\n<p style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">具有本品应有的色泽，燕窝呈晶莹透亮至微黄半透明，颜色均匀</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0cm;\">\n<td style=\"width: 56.2pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 1.0cm;\" width=\"75\">\n<p style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">滋味和气味</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 290.6pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 1.0cm;\" width=\"387\">\n<p style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">具有燕窝特有的香气，口</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">感糯绵，无异味</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0cm;\">\n<td style=\"width: 56.2pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 1.0cm;\" width=\"75\">\n<p style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">杂&nbsp;&nbsp; 质</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 290.6pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 1.0cm;\" width=\"387\">\n<p style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">无正常视力可</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">见</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">的外来杂质，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">允许燕窝带入少量的长度&le;5mm的绒毛、直径&le;0.4mm的黑点或长度&le;2mm的蛋膜存在</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5.3 理化指标</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">理化指标应符合表2的规定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 191.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 表2理化指标</span></strong></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"width: 467.55pt; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" width=\"6